means ‘those who will not accept will suffer’.

106
00:05:48,788 --> 00:05:51,208
But who will accept their hands will speak,

107
00:05:51,228 --> 00:05:52,499
their

108
00:05:52,559 --> 00:05:55,199
mouth will be shut and their hands will speak?

109
00:05:55,269 --> 00:05:57,459
This is exactly what happens in Sahaja Yoga

110
00:05:57,538 --> 00:06:00,497
that once you get your Self-realisation

111
00:06:00,543 --> 00:06:03,947
you can feel those subtle centres within you.

112
00:06:03,983 --> 00:06:06,100
These subtle centres of energy

113
00:06:06,129 --> 00:06:07,819
are seven in number

114
00:06:07,843 --> 00:06:15,754
and are acting for giving us all kinds of energies.

115
00:06:15,803 --> 00:06:18,670
Now the problem is how to make

116
