136
00:07:18,821 --> 00:07:21,581
Now there are three Nadis also

137
00:07:21,632 --> 00:07:24,310
Left, Right and Centre.

138
00:07:24,331 --> 00:07:27,139
Left is called as Ida Nadi,

139
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:28,939
right as Pingala

140
00:07:29,019 --> 00:07:36,050
