141
00:07:38,982 --> 00:07:41,572
Kabira has described it very clearly

142
00:07:41,632 --> 00:07:44,518
and it is in the Granth Sahib

143
00:07:44,538 --> 00:07:48,088
written down but nobody tries to understand

144
00:07:48,129 --> 00:07:49,648
or to go beyond the words.

145
00:07:49,668 --> 00:07:52,818
