212
00:11:38,721 --> 00:11:43,461
Now this centre is very important

213
00:11:43,501 --> 00:11:46,322
because it gives energy to our liver,

214
00:11:46,371 --> 00:11:49,313
to pancreas,

215
00:11:49,341 --> 00:11:52,883
