But I wouldn’t say that it’s something great

1058
00:50:05,488 --> 00:50:09,097
that I should know because I just know without any work,

1059
00:50:09,092 --> 00:50:11,556
without any thinking,

1060
00:50:11,577 --> 00:50:15,259
without any managing. Just automatically I know everything.

1061
00:50:15,327 --> 00:50:18,867
So, once you become that, you don’t have to worry.

1062
00:50:18,916 --> 00:50:23,817
Now, for example, I know, also, a lady doctor in Delhi,

1063
00:50:23,856 --> 00:50:25,485
no in Bombay.

1064
00:50:25,496 --> 00:50:28,295
She is the one who is a surgeon.

1065
00:50:28,297 --> 00:50:34,652
She said, “Mother I could know that this man has tumour,

1066
00:50:34,652 --> 00:50:38,652
very much low in his brains but it will come out.”

1067
00:50:38,663 --> 00:50:42,402
So, she said, “Then I was just giving vibrations first.

1068
00:50:42,416 --> 00:50:45,059
I said let me try first the vibrations on that.”

1069
00:50:45,056 --> 00:50:47,659
They said, “No, No, there is no tumour on that side.”

1070
00:50:47,677 --> 00:50:50,489
She said, “It is here. I know I can feel it; it is here.”

1071
00:50:50,487 --> 00:50:52,818
They wouldn’t, they started arguing with her

1072
00:50:52,846 --> 00:50:55,364
and then they found out the tumour where she said,

1073
00:50:55,376 --> 00:50:56,753
exactly there.

1074
00:50:56,766 --> 00:50:58,094
They said, “How do you know?”

1075
00:50:58,115 --> 00:51:00,322
She said, “I don’t know how do I know.”

1076
00:51:00,346 --> 00:51:03,474
So even the children can tell where is the problem,

1077
00:51:03,476 --> 00:51:07,804
in your head, in your brain, what is happening.

1078
00:51:07,804 --> 00:51:13,155
Now to look after your brain is very important that you don’t go into imbalances

1079
00:51:13,146 --> 00:51:14,916
because if you go into imbalance,

1080
00:51:14,965 --> 00:51:18,650
your right side will develop or your left side will develop.

1081
00:51:18,668 --> 00:51:20,929
Actually, the right side develops on the left

1082
00:51:20,938 --> 00:51:23,280
and the left side develops on the right.

1083
00:51:23,257 --> 00:51:26,668
Now also I don’t know how far the medical science has gone

1084
00:51:26,717 --> 00:51:30,608
up to the understanding as to left and right side

1085
00:51:30,668 --> 00:51:34,434
are two different complementary systems.

1086
00:51:34,489 --> 00:51:36,949
I don’t know if that they accept, do they?

1087
00:51:40,282 --> 00:51:46,045
But in Sahaja Yoga you will discover that there are two complementary systems.

1088
00:51:48,275 --> 00:51:51,119
One is right sided; one is left sided.

1089
00:51:51,135 --> 00:51:55,259
And when the right side is too much then the left side might act

1090
00:51:55,259 --> 00:51:58,559
or when the left side is too much, then right side may act.

1091
00:51:58,568 --> 00:52:01,159
You see it’s a complimentary two systems

1092
00:52:01,228 --> 00:52:03,847
and if you go on one system all the time

1093
00:52:03,896 --> 00:52:07,097
then you become right sided or left sided.

1094
00:52:07,106 --> 00:52:09,907
Now left sided are the people who are not futuristic

1095
00:52:09,916 --> 00:52:13,436
but who are the people who live in the past.

1096
00:52:13,445 --> 00:52:17,036
Now of course I don’t want to, just now, discuss about it very much

1097
00:52:17,059 --> 00:52:21,862
because it’s also more confusing for people.

1098
00:52:21,869 --> 00:52:23,521
Because they don’t want to believe

1099
00:52:23,539 --> 00:52:25,918
that there is something like dead souls

1100
00:52:25,958 --> 00:52:32,512
or they don’t want to believe in the viruses being dead vegetables

1101
00:52:32,516 --> 00:52:35,764
and things like that but it is.

1102
00:52:35,777 --> 00:52:37,213
On the left-hand side,

1103
00:52:37,204 --> 00:52:40,463
we have got all our past since our creation.

1104
00:52:40,463 --> 00:52:42,875
So, if somebody gets virus you give antibiotics,

1105
00:52:42,889 --> 00:52:45,894
you do what you like, it won’t go.

1106
00:52:45,918 --> 00:52:48,570
Only Sahaja Yoga can drive it out.

1107
00:52:48,570 --> 00:52:51,735
Only through Sahaja Yoga you can cure viruses

1108
00:52:51,750 --> 00:52:54,659
because only Sahaja Yoga can act on the left side.

1109
00:52:54,670 --> 00:52:59,829
Many mad people, crazy people have been cured through Sahaja Yoga.

1110
00:52:59,840 --> 00:53:05,853
Also, it gives you a good idea about

1111
00:53:05,849 --> 00:53:08,914
how you can show people,

1112
00:53:08,923 --> 00:53:11,492
who is mad and who is not mad.

1113
00:53:11,494 --> 00:53:14,563
Like I had a program in Pune in the beginning

1114
00:53:14,563 --> 00:53:20,943
and they arranged it in a hall which was owned by some Brahmins.

1115
00:53:20,976 --> 00:53:24,230
So, when I went there, they said, “No, no, She is not a Brahmin

1116
00:53:24,215 --> 00:53:25,880
so we can’t give Her the hall.

1117
00:53:25,891 --> 00:53:27,739
So, Sahaja Yogis were mischievous,

1118
00:53:27,771 --> 00:53:30,989
they said, “All right, we will give it in the newspaper that they are refusing

1119
00:53:31,001 --> 00:53:32,489
because She is not a Brahmin.”

1120
00:53:32,492 --> 00:53:35,208
“No, no, don’t do like that we will have it.”

1121
00:53:35,231 --> 00:53:37,989
So, I didn’t know what was happening behind the back.

1122
00:53:38,048 --> 00:53:39,809
When I went there, I was sitting there.

1123
00:53:39,818 --> 00:53:44,273
Very interesting I saw about twenty-five people sitting in front of me shaking

1124
00:53:44,262 --> 00:53:45,842
like this

1125
00:53:45,853 --> 00:53:46,998
“Mother, stop it, stop it

1126
00:53:47,012 --> 00:53:48,393
we know Your powers, stop it.”

1127
00:53:48,393 --> 00:53:50,163
I said, “I am not doing anything, you are….”

1128
00:53:50,182 --> 00:53:54,030
They said, “Now, also there are people who are shaking like this.”

1129
00:53:54,023 --> 00:53:56,460
So, I said, “Ask them, who they are?”

1130
00:53:56,476 --> 00:54:00,739
They said, “We are certified mad from Thana.

1131
00:54:00,746 --> 00:54:03,106
We have come here with our superintendent

1132
00:54:03,126 --> 00:54:05,670
because You had cured one mad man.”

1133
00:54:05,679 --> 00:54:09,130
“So”, they said, “Are we also mad?” “Yes, there is something wrong.”

1134
00:54:09,148 --> 00:54:10,719
So, the thing was

1135
00:54:10,739 --> 00:54:13,998
they were thinking the Brahmins are the highest or something like that.

1136
00:54:14,028 --> 00:54:16,382
Is all nonsensical ideas

1137
00:54:16,411 --> 00:54:19,190
because Brahmin is that which knows the Brahma,

1138
00:54:19,211 --> 00:54:21,889
which knows All Pervading Power.

1139
00:54:21,911 --> 00:54:25,742
And because of these funny ideas, they have tortured all the saints.

1140
00:54:25,802 --> 00:54:28,260
Specially in Maharashtra

1141
00:54:28,260 --> 00:54:32,179
people have tortured all the saints all the time.

1142
00:54:32,204 --> 00:54:35,423
So, where you have so many saints

1143
00:54:35,474 --> 00:54:36,636
and so many people

1144
00:54:36,646 --> 00:54:40,081
then you must know that it was just to work out

1145
00:54:40,099 --> 00:54:43,451
the brains of these close-minded people.

1146
00:54:43,478 --> 00:54:48,699
But to open them out is only possible I think when they are in difficulties.

1147
00:54:48,759 --> 00:54:51,695
When they are not in difficulties they don’t want to accept.

1148
00:54:51,708 --> 00:54:54,704
Supposing they are sick then they will come to Me.

1149
00:54:54,717 --> 00:54:58,333
Now if you cure somebody sick, you see once he is cured, he is finished.

1150
00:54:58,338 --> 00:55:01,684
He doesn’t do any Sahaja Yoga; he doesn’t want to help anyone.

1151
00:55:01,693 --> 00:55:05,853
But if there is a person who is healthy,

1152
00:55:05,884 --> 00:55:08,188
who is perfectly all right

1153
00:55:08,184 --> 00:55:10,639
and who is knowledgeable,

1154
00:55:10,634 --> 00:55:13,079
if he comes to Sahaja Yoga, he will be such a help

1155
00:55:13,079 --> 00:55:17,581
to this, I should say, to this poor country.

1156
00:55:17,588 --> 00:55:20,880
This country is suffering from tremendous poverty.

1157
00:55:20,898 --> 00:55:22,744
Now only saying,

1158
00:55:22,773 --> 00:55:26,164
“Garibi Hatao, Garibi Hatao, Garibi Hatao” (“Eliminate poverty!”)

1159
00:55:26,155 --> 00:55:29,554
I know of one gentleman who was a great corrupt fellow

1160
00:55:29,574 --> 00:55:33,030
and who used to live in one room with a little cot.

1161
00:55:33,050 --> 00:55:34,882
I said, “Why do you live like this?”

1162
00:55:34,900 --> 00:55:37,822
He said, “Because, everybody is garib [poor] so I want to live like garib.”

1163
00:55:37,831 --> 00:55:40,052
I said, “Why don’t you give all this money to these garibs?

1164
00:55:40,070 --> 00:55:41,911
Why are you lying like this?”

1165
00:55:41,931 --> 00:55:44,550
He said, “All right, you suggest to me any organisation

1166
00:55:44,621 --> 00:55:48,931
which is absolutely above board and I will move.”

1167
00:55:48,931 --> 00:55:51,588
That was a difficult thing, a decision.

1168
00:55:51,590 --> 00:55:52,847
But what I am trying to say

1169
00:55:52,880 --> 00:55:55,289
only by saying people are garib, garib,

1170
00:55:55,349 --> 00:55:57,679
you have to attend to that

1171
00:55:57,699 --> 00:56:00,179
and is only possible through Sahaja Yoga.

1172
00:56:00,190 --> 00:56:01,320
How?

1173
00:56:01,326 --> 00:56:05,885
Sahaja Yoga is practiced mostly by middle class.

1174
00:56:05,905 --> 00:56:10,275
Both the sides are – one side are the poor, another side are the rich.

1175
00:56:10,346 --> 00:56:13,655
Rich are very few. But more by the middle class.

1176
00:56:13,668 --> 00:56:17,545
Then it’s like a river which expands on both the sides

1177
00:56:17,565 --> 00:56:22,092
This time I was, I mean, I have been always thinking that

1178
00:56:22,094 --> 00:56:24,905
I have to do something for the poor people,

1179
00:56:24,932 --> 00:56:28,324
something, always and I have done also, on my own,

1180
00:56:28,338 --> 00:56:31,494
but I wanted Sahaja Yogis to contribute, Indian Sahaja Yogis.

1181
00:56:31,489 --> 00:56:34,143
So, I told them I want to start a place

1182
00:56:34,139 --> 00:56:37,878
where we could have these women

1183
00:56:37,873 --> 00:56:41,963
who are standing on the roads with their children asking for alms.

1184
00:56:42,007 --> 00:56:44,814
We can have something to help them.

1185
00:56:44,834 --> 00:56:48,018
Immediately, I was surprised Sahaja Yogis contributed to me

1186
00:56:48,047 --> 00:56:52,237
for that and I was so amazed at their enthusiasm.

1187
00:56:52,260 --> 00:56:54,061
I said, “This is the generosity.

1188
00:56:54,112 --> 00:56:57,039
This generosity that has come to Sahaja Yogis.”

1189
00:56:57,050 --> 00:57:01,630
And then when they said, “Mother this is we have got all this through Sahaja Yoga

1190
00:57:01,650 --> 00:57:05,710
We have improved so much that we don’t have to worry.”

1191
00:57:05,744 --> 00:57:10,063
And they so generously, I mean a person becomes extremely generous.

1192
00:57:10,083 --> 00:57:12,143
He becomes very peaceful;

1193
00:57:12,164 --> 00:57:16,514
he becomes generous and he starts enjoying the generosity.

1194
00:57:16,518 --> 00:57:19,014
I mean people earn such a lot of money.

1195
00:57:19,009 --> 00:57:21,668
Everything they should do there is no harm.

1196
00:57:21,739 --> 00:57:24,438
In Sahaja Yoga, there is nothing like sanyasa.

1197
00:57:24,498 --> 00:57:26,242
Nobody has to take sanyas.

1198
00:57:26,228 --> 00:57:29,003
Nobody has to go out of his family,

1199
00:57:29,032 --> 00:57:33,974
out of his … nothing. It’s all here. Why to go anywhere?

1200
00:57:33,974 --> 00:57:37,440
So, you have to be a very normal person.

1201
00:57:37,489 --> 00:57:39,789
But one thing is important,

1202
00:57:39,840 --> 00:57:44,673
you must have the pure desire to get your Realisation.

1203
00:57:44,692 --> 00:57:48,731
If you don’t have that pure Realisation then it doesn’t work out.

1204
00:57:48,742 --> 00:57:50,574
Apart from that it might work

1205
00:57:50,592 --> 00:57:52,213
but you go on dropping down

1206
00:57:52,224 --> 00:57:54,786
because if you want to make money out of Sahaja Yoga

1207
00:57:54,775 --> 00:57:58,976
or if you want to, say, achieve some power out of it.

1208
00:57:58,974 --> 00:58:00,282
You see, you are so powerful

1209
00:58:00,304 --> 00:58:03,547
that you don’t have to ask for power or anything.

1210
00:58:03,572 --> 00:58:07,097
You don’t know how it works and how it gives.

1211
00:58:07,103 --> 00:58:09,887
First of all, only we have to believe

1212
00:58:09,887 --> 00:58:15,108
that we are reflections of God Almighty.

1213
00:58:15,128 --> 00:58:17,668
We're not just human beings.

1214
00:58:17,677 --> 00:58:21,159
Specially, to be born in India

1215
00:58:21,168 --> 00:58:23,141
you must have done lots of punyas,

1216
00:58:23,168 --> 00:58:27,509
otherwise you cannot be born in this great country I can tell you.

1217
00:58:27,539 --> 00:58:31,188
All this, you see, is all nonsense that is going on,

1218
00:58:31,199 --> 00:58:34,757
is just skirmishes on the periphery,

1219
00:58:34,780 --> 00:58:38,769
but if you see the culture,

1220
00:58:38,820 --> 00:58:42,061
the love, affection we have,

1221
00:58:42,074 --> 00:58:45,351
the understanding of value system we have,

1222
00:58:45,355 --> 00:58:46,621
you can’t imagine it.

1223
00:58:46,646 --> 00:58:48,670
When you go abroad, you are amazed.

1224
00:58:48,686 --> 00:58:51,590
you don’t know how to tell them.

1225
00:58:51,605 --> 00:58:52,920
They're so stupid,

1226
00:58:52,990 --> 00:58:56,871
I tell you, very stupid people, nothing to learn from them.

1227
00:58:56,931 --> 00:59:01,820
I have been fighting with the stupidity of people specially Americans.

1228
00:59:01,880 --> 00:59:06,023
I'm surprised, I think that they are not yet grown up as human beings.

1229
00:59:06,045 --> 00:59:08,123
The way they talk, the way they understand.

1230
00:59:08,135 --> 00:59:11,818
They only like people who will come and tell them stories

1231
00:59:11,844 --> 00:59:14,574
and make fool out of them, make lot of money.

1232
00:59:14,625 --> 00:59:16,897
To me they said, “We cannot take to Sahaja Yoga.”

1233
00:59:16,876 --> 00:59:17,917
I said, “Why?”

1234
00:59:17,905 --> 00:59:19,193
“Because you don’t take money,

1235
00:59:19,206 --> 00:59:20,945
what is your validity?

1236
00:59:20,956 --> 00:59:23,485
If you don’t take money then you have no validity,

1237
00:59:23,545 --> 00:59:26,283
why should we believe in you because …”

1238
00:59:26,286 --> 00:59:30,073
I said, “Supposing I take money, then?” “Then we can prosecute you.”

1239
00:59:30,088 --> 00:59:32,813
I said, “Go and prosecute all these people who have looted you”.

1240
00:59:32,827 --> 00:59:34,933
Nobody could prosecute them.

1241
00:59:34,947 --> 00:59:40,619
So, this is we should not look to them for understanding of life.

1242
00:59:40,623 --> 00:59:42,018
They have not yet understood.

1243
00:59:42,038 --> 00:59:44,179
We have to look to ourselves.

1244
00:59:44,184 --> 00:59:46,250
We have such a heritage.

1245
00:59:46,284 --> 00:59:48,409
You can imagine, thousands of years back,

1246
00:59:48,403 --> 00:59:50,443
we have been talking of Brahma,

1247
00:59:50,494 --> 00:59:55,818
we have been talking of absolute truth.

1248
00:59:55,838 --> 00:59:59,118
In what country they have this kind of knowledge.

1249
00:59:59,118 --> 01:00:00,105
No country.

1250
01:00:00,108 --> 01:00:04,472
So, first of all we should be very proud to be an Indian.

1251
01:00:04,489 --> 01:00:05,911
That’s very important.

1252
01:00:05,922 --> 01:00:08,661
Even Sahaja Yogis from abroad they dress up like Indians

1253
01:00:08,702 --> 01:00:10,791
and they have taken to our culture,

1254
01:00:10,791 --> 01:00:12,478
our style of culture.

1255
01:00:12,467 --> 01:00:14,833
I need not tell you about the Western Culture

1256
01:00:14,893 --> 01:00:17,507
as I was really shocked.

1257
01:00:17,514 --> 01:00:20,195
Then I thought I better write down something about them

1258
01:00:20,204 --> 01:00:21,965
as a witness whatever I saw.

1259
01:00:21,963 --> 01:00:24,344
So, there is nothing to learn from them,

1260
01:00:24,414 --> 01:00:28,353
but one day will come, they have to come here.

1261
01:00:28,363 --> 01:00:30,822
All the doctors have to come here.

1262
01:00:30,851 --> 01:00:34,902
I am very thankful, very, very thankful

1263
01:00:34,911 --> 01:00:38,672
to this Indian Medical Association especially.

1264
01:00:38,719 --> 01:00:44,382
I never expected and I am very grateful to them for this

1265
01:00:44,385 --> 01:00:48,432
because I know in this country if the doctors take it up,

1266
01:00:48,452 --> 01:00:52,037
all over the world they will have to understand

1267
01:00:58,125 --> 01:01:04,918
the value of our knowledge of life and of Medical Science.

1268
01:01:04,918 --> 01:01:08,389
I would say that I have seen so many people sitting here

1269
01:01:08,429 --> 01:01:09,790
I don’t know how many are doctors,

1270
01:01:09,798 --> 01:01:13,480
how many are from industries and how many are Sahaja Yogis.

1271
01:01:13,476 --> 01:01:16,990
Whatever it is, one has to know that all of us

1272
01:01:17,003 --> 01:01:20,614
are blessed by the same reflection of God Almighty

1273
01:01:20,673 --> 01:01:23,582
within ourselves which we should experience.

1274
01:01:23,606 --> 01:01:27,072
After that you will tell me what has happened to you,

1275
01:01:27,076 --> 01:01:30,202
what you have felt and what you had.

1276
01:01:30,217 --> 01:01:34,012
It’s a thing, is a matter of your right to have it.

1277
01:01:34,019 --> 01:01:36,642
It’s your right to have that power

1278
01:01:36,653 --> 01:01:39,554
but you have to ask for it.

1279
01:01:39,614 --> 01:01:42,333
If you don’t ask for it, I cannot force it on you.

1280
01:01:42,384 --> 01:01:44,333
Nobody can force it on you.

1281
01:01:44,393 --> 01:01:46,335
It is a very spontaneous happening

1282
01:01:46,414 --> 01:01:51,224
and it works out, so fast, so fast.

1283
01:01:51,224 --> 01:01:53,277
I must tell you in Russia,

1284
01:01:53,284 --> 01:01:55,994
this hall of course has fallen short

